<wxs module="filter" src="../../utils/numFr.wxs"></wxs>
<nav-bar navbar-data='{{nvabarData}}'></nav-bar>
<view class="member-bg">
  <view class='bg-top'>
    <view class='top1'>
      <image src='../../images/huangguan2.png'></image>
    </view>
    <view class='top2'>超级会员开通</view>
    <view class='top3'>开通会员 特权体验 精彩无限</view>
  </view>

  <view class='member-rights'>
    <view class='right-title'>会员专属权益</view>
    <view>
      <view class='rights-item'>
        <image src='../../images/hyzxj.png'></image>
        <view class='right'>
          <view class='color1 font1'>会员专享价</view>
          <view>会员可享有所有商品会员折扣价购买</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class='rights-item'>
        <image src='../../images/zzsfl.png'></image>
        <view class='right'>
          <view class='color1 font1'>周周送福利</view>
          <view>会员每周会收到专属会员桔子礼包（15个）</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class='rights-item'>
        <image src='../../images/hyzsq.png'></image>
        <view class='right'>
          <view class='color1 font1'>会员专属区</view>
          <view>带有会员专属标签的商品仅限会员购买</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class='rights-item'>
        <image src='../../images/zskf.png'></image>
        <view class='right'>
          <view class='color1 font1'>专属客服</view>
          <view>专属客服权益仅限会员专享，会员享有优先客服通道，无需排队会员配备专属微信客服顾问，提供更专业、优质的服务与咨询（1对1客服）</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='cards-list winner'>
    <view class='cards-title'>选择会员版本</view>
    <view>
      <view class='card-item' wx:for="{{dataList}}" wx:key="{{index}}" wx:for-item="item" bindtap='cardClick' data-card='{{item}}'>
        <view class='card card1'>
          <view class='origin-price' wx:if="{{item.skuId == 'YEAR_CARD'}}">原价¥{{item.originalPrice/100}}</view>
          <view class='card-name'>{{item.skuName}}</view>
          <view class='card-price'>¥ {{filter.toFix(item.price)}}</view>
          <image class='selected' wx:if="{{selectedCard.id == item.id}}" src='../../images/xuanzhong.png'></image>
        </view>
        <view class='card-bottom'>赠送{{item.point}}桔子</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <form bindsubmit="collectFormIds" report-submit="true">
    <button form-type="submit" class='buy' bindtap='buy'>立即购买</button>
  </form>

  <button class='buy share' open-type="share">分享</button>

</view>